{
  "Applications in Economics (input-output models)": "经济学应用(投入-产出模型)",
  "This lesson covers the fundamental measures of center used to analyze and summarize data sets. You'll learn how to calculate and apply the mean, median, and mode, and understand when each is most appropriate.": "这个课程涵盖了分析和总结数据集的中心的基本测量方法。 您将学会如何计算和应用平均值、 中位数和模式, 并了解何时最合适 。",
  "A 2-sector economy has consumption matrix A = [[0.2, 0.3],[0.4, 0.1]]. What is I - A?": "一个部门经济体的消费矩阵A=[0.2,0.3],[0.4,0.1]。",
  "I - A = [[1,0],[0,1]] - [[0.2,0.3],[0.4,0.1]] = [[1-0.2, 0-0.3],[0-0.4, 1-0.1]] = [[0.8, -0.3],[-0.4, 0.9]].": "- A = [[1,0,[0,1] - [0.2.0.3],[0.4,0.1]] = [[1-0.2,0-0.3],[0-0.4,1-0.1] = [0.8,-0.3],[-0.4,0.9]]。",
  "For the consumption matrix A = [[0.2, 0.3],[0.4, 0.1]], what is det(I - A)?": "对于消费矩阵A = [[0.2,0.3],[0.4,0.1]],执行(I - A)是什么?",
  "I - A = [[0.8, -0.3],[-0.4, 0.9]]. det(I - A) = 0.8*0.9 - (-0.3)*(-0.4) = 0.72 - 0.12 = 0.60. Since the determinant is positive, the system has a unique solution.": "- A=[[0.8,-0.3],[-0.4,0.9]]。 det(I-A) = 0.8*0.9 - (-0.3)* (-0.4) = 0.72 - 0.12 = 0.60。由于决定因素是积极的,这个系统有一个独特的解决办法。",
  "In portfolio theory, the variance of a portfolio with weight vector w and covariance matrix C is given by w^T C w. If C = [[4,1],[1,9]] and w = [0.5, 0.5]^T, what is the portfolio variance?": "在投资组合理论中,具有重量矢量和共变矩阵C的投资组合差异由wT Cw给出。 如果C=[[4]1]、[1]、[1]]和w=[0.5、0.5] 和(w)=[0.5、0.5]+T,投资组合差异是什么?",
  "Cw = [[4,1],[1,9]]*[0.5,0.5]^T = [2.5, 5]^T. w^T Cw = [0.5,0.5]*[2.5,5]^T = 0.5*2.5 + 0.5*5 = 1.25 + 2.5 = 3.75. The portfolio variance is 3.75.": "Cw = [[4,1,[1,9]] * [0.5,0.5] T = [2.5,5] T. wT Cw = [0.5,0.5] * [2.5,5] T = 0.5*2.5 + 0.5*5 = 1.25 + 2.5 = 3.75 组合差额为3.75。",
  "In game theory, a payoff matrix is P = [[3,-1],[-2,4]]. In a zero-sum game, if Player 1 chooses row 1 and Player 2 chooses column 2, what is Player 1's payoff?": "在游戏理论上,回报矩阵是 P = [[3,-1],[2,4]。在零和游戏中,如果玩家1选择第1行,玩家2选择第2栏,玩家1的回报是什么?",
  "The payoff matrix entry P[1][2] gives Player 1's payoff when Player 1 chooses row 1 and Player 2 chooses column 2. P[1][2] = -1, meaning Player 1 loses 1 unit.": "回报矩阵条目 P[1][2] 给玩家 1 的回报, 当玩家 1 选择第 1 行, 玩家 2 选择 第 2 栏, P[1][2] = - 1, 意味着玩家 1 损失 1 个单位 。",
  "What is the 'Leontief input-output model' in economics?": "经济学中什么是“Leontief 投入产出模型”?",
  "The Leontief input-output model represents an economy as interconnected sectors where each sector's output is consumed by other sectors. The linear system x = Ax + d captures how production must satisfy both inter-industry demand (Ax) and final demand (d).": "Leontief投入-产出模式代表着一个经济作为相互关联的部门,每个部门的产出由其他部门消费,线性系统x = Ax + d 说明生产如何既满足行业间需求(Ax)又满足最终需求(d)。",
  "What is the 'Leontief inverse' in the input-output model?": "在输入输出模型中,“ Leontief 反向”是什么?",
  "The Leontief inverse (I - A)^{-1} can be expanded as I + A + A^2 + A^3 + ... (when convergent), capturing both direct and indirect input requirements. It maps external demand d to total production x = (I-A)^{-1}d.": "Leontifef 反(I - A)  -1} 可扩展为 I + A + A + A + + A + + + A 3 +... (当聚合时) , 包含直接和间接投入要求。 它绘制了外部需求d 到总生产x = (I-A) = 1 }d。",
  "What is a 'covariance matrix' in financial economics?": "在金融经济学中,什么是“共变矩阵”?",
  "The covariance matrix C has diagonal entries C_{ii} = Var(r_i) (the variance of asset i's return) and off-diagonal entries C_{ij} = Cov(r_i, r_j). It is always symmetric and positive semi-definite.": "共变矩阵C有对角条目Cii} = Var(r_i)(资产 i 回报的差异) 和对角条目Cij} = Cov(r_i,r_j) 。它总是对称和正半确定性。",
  "What is a 'transition matrix' in economic Markov models?": "经济模式马可夫(Markov)的“过渡矩阵”是什么?",
  "In economic Markov models (e.g., brand switching, employment status), the transition matrix T has entry T_{ij} giving the probability of moving from state j to state i. Each column sums to 1.": "在经济模式Markov(如品牌转换、就业状况)中,过渡矩阵T有条目Tij},从国家j到国家i的概率。",
  "What is 'Markowitz portfolio optimization'?": "马可维茨组合优化是什么?",
  "Markowitz portfolio optimization minimizes portfolio variance w^T C w subject to constraints on expected return w^T mu = target and budget w^T 1 = 1. The solution uses the covariance matrix C and expected return vector mu.": "Markowitz组合优化将投资组合差异最小化(w)T Cw,但受预期回报(w)T mu = 目标和预算(w)T 1 = 1. 限制,解决方案使用共变矩阵C和预期回报矢量mu。",
  "An economist models a 2-sector economy with consumption matrix A = [[0.1, 0.4],[0.3, 0.2]] and final demand d = [100, 200]^T. They compute I - A = [[0.9, -0.4],[-0.3, 0.8]]. What is det(I - A)?": "经济学家以消费矩阵A=[[0.1,0.4],[0.3,0.2]]和最终需求d=[100,200]<T。 他们计算I -A =[[0.9,-0.4],[-0.3,0.8]]。",
  "det(I - A) = 0.9*0.8 - (-0.4)*(-0.3) = 0.72 - 0.12 = 0.60. Since this is positive, the Leontief inverse exists and the economy can satisfy the demand.": "det(I - A) = 0.9*0.8 - (-0.4) * (-0.3) = 0.72 - 0.12 = 0.60。由于这是正数,Leontief 倒数存在,经济可以满足需求。",
  "Continuing from the previous economy with (I-A) = [[0.9,-0.4],[-0.3,0.8]] and d = [100,200]^T, the economist computes (I-A)^{-1} = (1/0.6)*[[0.8,0.4],[0.3,0.9]]. What is the total production vector x?": "(I-A) = [0.9,-0.4],[-0.3,0.8] 和 d = [100,200] T,经济学家计算 (I-A) -1} = (1/0.6)* [0.8,0.4],[0.3,0.9]]。",
  "x = (I-A)^{-1}d = (1/0.6)*[[0.8,0.4],[0.3,0.9]]*[100,200]^T = (1/0.6)*[0.8*100+0.4*200, 0.3*100+0.9*200]^T = (1/0.6)*[160, 210]^T = [266.67, 350]^T.": "x = (I-A) -1}d = (1/0.6)* [0.8,0.4],[0.3,0.9]* [100,200] T = (1/0.6)* * [0.8*100+0.4*200,0.3*100+0.9*200] T = (1/0.6)* [160,210] T = [266.67,350]",
  "A financial analyst has 3 assets with covariance matrix C = [[4,2,0],[2,9,3],[0,3,16]]. They want to invest equally in all three (w = [1/3,1/3,1/3]^T). What is the portfolio variance w^T C w?": "金融分析员有3个资产,其共同矩阵C=[[4,2,0],[2,9],[3,16]]。他们希望对所有三个资产进行同等投资(w =[1,3,1,3,1,1,3,3,3]。",
  "Cw = [[4,2,0],[2,9,3],[0,3,16]]*[1/3,1/3,1/3]^T = [6/3, 14/3, 19/3]^T = [2, 14/3, 19/3]^T. w^T Cw = (1/3)*2 + (1/3)*(14/3) + (1/3)*(19/3) = 2/3 + 14/9 + 19/9 = 6/9 + 14/9 + 19/9 = 39/9 = 4.33.": "Cw = [[4,2,0]、[2,9,3]、[0,3,3]、[3,3,3]、* [1,3,1,3,1,3,3]、*** T = [6,3,14,3,19/3] T = [2,14,3,19] T = [2,14,3,19/3,19/3] T = [3,14,19] T = [3,14,3,19] T = [2,14,3,19/3,19] T = [3,19,19] T = [2,14,19/3,19/3] T. w,w w,w 3,2 +(1/3) * (14/3) * (19/3) + 1,3,* (19/3) = 2/3 + 14/9+ 19/9 = 6/9+ 14,9 + 19/9 = 39/9 = 4.33。",
  "An economist uses a Markov chain to model employment. The transition matrix is T = [[0.9, 0.3],[0.1, 0.7]] (columns: employed, unemployed). Starting with 80% employed and 20% unemployed, what is the employment rate after one period?": "经济学家用Markov链来模拟就业。过渡矩阵是T = [0.9,0.3],[0.1,0.7] (校友:就业、失业)。从80%的就业开始,20%失业,一个时期后的就业率是多少?",
  "x_1 = T*x_0 = [[0.9,0.3],[0.1,0.7]]*[0.8,0.2]^T = [0.9*0.8+0.3*0.2, 0.1*0.8+0.7*0.2]^T = [0.72+0.06, 0.08+0.14]^T = [0.78, 0.22]^T. Employment rate is 78%.": "x_1 = T*x_0 = [0.9,0.3],[0.1,0.7]* [0.8,0.2]}**T = [0.9*0.8+0.3*0.2,0.1*0.8+0.7*0.2] = [0.72+0.06,0.08+0.14] ] = T =[0.78,0.22]。就业率为78%。",
  "A game theorist analyzes a 2-player zero-sum game with payoff matrix P = [[4, -2],[-1, 3]]. Player 1 uses mixed strategy [p, 1-p] and Player 2 uses mixed strategy [q, 1-q]. What is Player 1's expected payoff as a function of p and q?": "游戏理论家用支付矩阵 P = [[4, -2], [1, 3] 来分析玩家零和游戏。玩家 1 使用混合策略[p, 1 - p],玩家 2 使用混合策略[q, 1 - q]。玩家 1 的预期回报作为p和 q的函数是什么?",
  "The expected payoff is the weighted sum of all entries: E = p*q*P[1][1] + p*(1-q)*P[1][2] + (1-p)*q*P[2][1] + (1-p)*(1-q)*P[2][2] = 4pq - 2p(1-q) - (1-p)q + 3(1-p)(1-q).": "预期的回报是所有条目的加权总和:E=p*q*P[1][1]+p*(1-q)*P[1][2]+(1-p)*q*P[2][1]+(1-p)*(1-p)(1-q)*P[2][2]=4pq-2p(1-q) -(1-p)q+3(1-1-p)(1-q)。",
  "A pension fund manager has a portfolio of 2 assets with expected returns mu = [8%, 12%]^T and covariance matrix C = [[4, -1],[-1, 9]]. What is the expected return of the portfolio with weights w = [0.6, 0.4]^T?": "养恤基金管理人拥有2个资产组合,预期回报率为[8%,12%] T和共同变量矩阵C = [[4,-1,1,[1,9]]]。",
  "Expected return = w^T * mu = 0.6*8% + 0.4*12% = 4.8% + 4.8% = 9.6%. The portfolio expected return is a weighted average of individual asset returns.": "预期回报 = wQT * mu = 0.6*8% + 0.4*12% = 4.8% + 4.8% + 4.8% = 9.6% 投资组合预期回报是个人资产回报的加权平均数。",
  "An economist studies the long-run behavior of a brand-switching Markov chain with T = [[0.7, 0.4],[0.3, 0.6]]. The steady-state vector q satisfies Tq = q and q1 + q2 = 1. What is the steady-state distribution?": "一位经济学家研究了以T = [0.7,0.4],[0.3,0.6]]。稳定状态矢量q 满足 Tq = q 和 q1 + q2 = 1. 稳定状态分布是什么?",
  "From Tq = q: 0.7*q1 + 0.4*q2 = q1 gives -0.3*q1 + 0.4*q2 = 0, so q2 = (3/4)*q1. With q1 + q2 = 1: q1 + (3/4)*q1 = 1, so (7/4)*q1 = 1, giving q1 = 4/7 and q2 = 3/7.": "从Tq = q: 0.7* q1 + 0.4* q2 = q1 = 0.3* q1 + 0.4* q2 = 0, 所以 q2 = (3/4* q1 = 1: q1 + q2 = 1: q1 + (3/4* q1 = 1, 所以 (7/4* q1 = 1, 给 q1 = 4/7 和 q2 = 3/7)。",
  "A trade economist models 3 countries exchanging goods. The exchange matrix is E = [[0.6,0.2,0.1],[0.3,0.5,0.3],[0.1,0.3,0.6]]. What percentage of Country 1's production stays within Country 1?": "E=[0.6,0.2.0.1],[0.3,0.5,0.3],[0.1,0.3,0.6]。",
  "In the exchange matrix, column 1 represents the distribution of Country 1's production. E[1][1] = 0.6 means 60% of Country 1's production stays in Country 1. The remaining 40% is exported (30% to Country 2, 10% to Country 3).": "在交换矩阵中,第1栏表示国家1的生产分布情况。E[1][1]=0.6表示国家1生产量的60%留在国家1。其余40%出口到国家2(30%出口到国家2,10%出口到国家3)。",
  "A supply chain manager uses the Leontief model for a 3-sector economy. If final demand for sector 2 increases by 10 units while sectors 1 and 3 stay the same, the change in total production is delta_x = (I-A)^{-1} * [0,10,0]^T. This equals the second column of (I-A)^{-1} multiplied by 10. Why?": "如果对部门2的最终需求增加10个单位,而部门1和3保持不变,总生产的变化是(I-A)x=(I-A)-1}*[0,10,0]T。这等于(I-A)-1}第二列乘以10。",
  "When you multiply a matrix M by a vector with only the j-th entry non-zero (value c), the result is c times the j-th column of M. So (I-A)^{-1}*[0,10,0]^T = 10 * (column 2 of (I-A)^{-1}), showing the ripple effect through all sectors.": "当将矩阵M乘以矢量时,只有j-th条目的非零(c值),结果乘以j-th列的 m. So. (I-A) -1 [0,10,0,0] T = 10 * (I-A) -1}第2栏),显示波纹效应贯穿所有部门。"
}